  RFC9069 [label="RFC9069
Support for Local RIB in the BGP
Monitoring Protocol (BMP)
2022", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="The BGP Monitoring Protocol (BMP) defines access to local Routing Information Bases (RIBs).  This document updates BMP (RFC 7854) by adding access to the Local Routing Information Base (Loc-RIB), as defined in RFC 4271.  The Loc-RIB contains the routes that have been selected by the local BGP speaker's Decision Process.", style=filled, fillcolor=green]; 

